All DNA repair-deficient, mutant cell lines are isogenic to the wild type cell line.

Both wild type and mutant DT40 cells were cultured at 39°C with 5% CO2 by using RPMI 1640 medium supplemented 10% fetal bovine serum, 1% chicken serum, 100 U/ml penicillin, and 100 U/ml streptomycin, 50 μM β -mercaptoethanol, and 2 mM L – glutamine [].
